{"tid":1759448,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠：「一國兩制」不只是一項合併","createTime":"2019-11-27T15:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T03:36:27.000Z","uid":81228,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2665c30daafa675adf932b103e57391bf208f787","tid":1759448,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20191127/s00010/c5b11184a8f5ad3e4009f7b3a4bb205a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20191127%2Fs00010%2Fc5b11184a8f5ad3e4009f7b3a4bb205a.jpg&h=2e06cda5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李嘉誠指出，對於一國兩制，總有意見分歧，但一路走來也還不錯。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n據路透社報道指，香港首富李嘉誠書面回覆近日所受到的指責，提到「在社交媒體的世界，有些人別有用心散播惡毒猜疑和假消息，破壞互信」，同時續指「對那些莫須有的指責，已經習慣了」，更強調「此時此刻要不招風雨，確實不易」。<br />\n<br />\n對於內地對香港日益加強的控制的情況，李嘉誠指出，對於一國兩制，總有意見分歧，但一路走來也還不錯。其發言人則表示，雙方須做實事，謀求制度創新，一國兩制不只是一項合併。<br />\n<br />\n年屆91歲的李嘉誠在今年9月，回應香港局勢時曾勸勉特區政府應對香港未來主人翁「網開一面」，期後受到內地以及香港親中黨派抨擊。中央政法委更在並其微信發表評論文章，批評李嘉誠的說法是「縱容犯罪」。此外，香港工聯會主席更在Facebook貼文嘲諷其為「曱甴王」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1574866848900&amp;issue=20191127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1574866848900%26issue%3D20191127&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DVA4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=3edad8aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1574866848900&amp;issue=20191127</a>"},{"pid":"48c2ec11fa1b80bac0a0c1b4a2b7518d3833de9f","tid":1759448,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ed4f58dd3beb139de7645e608205fecef1e33337","tid":1759448,"uid":132859,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:53:23.000Z","msg":"次主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6471be560a33d06343c1a22ad7842b6b6d873ed7","tid":1759448,